		<StreamGeometry x:Key="eye_tracking_regular">M8.24707 2C8.66128 2 8.99707 2.33579 8.99707 2.75C8.99707 3.1297 8.71492 3.44349 8.34884 3.49315L8.24707 3.5H4.74707C4.09986 3.5 3.56754 3.99187 3.50352 4.62219L3.49707 4.75V8.25234C3.49707 8.66655 3.16128 9.00234 2.74707 9.00234C2.36737 9.00234 2.05358 8.72018 2.00392 8.35411L1.99707 8.25234V4.75C1.99707 3.28747 3.13877 2.0916 4.57955 2.00502L4.74707 2H8.24707Z M3.49022 15.6482C3.44056 15.2822 3.12677 15 2.74707 15C2.36737 15 2.05358 15.2822 2.00392 15.6482L1.99707 15.75V19.2523L2.0025 19.4265C2.08889 20.8088 3.19641 21.9142 4.57955 21.9973L4.74707 22.0023H8.24707L8.34884 21.9955C8.71492 21.9458 8.99707 21.632 8.99707 21.2523C8.99707 20.8726 8.71492 20.5588 8.34884 20.5092L8.24707 20.5023H4.74707L4.61927 20.4959C4.03097 20.4361 3.56327 19.9684 3.50352 19.3801L3.49707 19.2523V15.75L3.49022 15.6482Z M21.9902 15.6482C21.9406 15.2822 21.6268 15 21.2471 15C20.8329 15 20.4971 15.3358 20.4971 15.75V19.2523L20.4906 19.3801C20.4266 20.0105 19.8943 20.5023 19.2471 20.5023H15.7471L15.6453 20.5092C15.2792 20.5588 14.9971 20.8726 14.9971 21.2523C14.9971 21.6665 15.3329 22.0023 15.7471 22.0023H19.2471L19.4146 21.9973C20.8554 21.9107 21.9971 20.7149 21.9971 19.2523V15.75L21.9902 15.6482Z M19.4146 2.00502L19.2471 2H15.7471L15.6453 2.00685C15.2792 2.05651 14.9971 2.3703 14.9971 2.75C14.9971 3.1297 15.2792 3.44349 15.6453 3.49315L15.7471 3.5H19.2471L19.3749 3.50645C19.9632 3.5662 20.4309 4.0339 20.4906 4.62219L20.4971 4.75V8.25234L20.5039 8.35411C20.5536 8.72018 20.8674 9.00234 21.2471 9.00234C21.6268 9.00234 21.9406 8.72018 21.9902 8.35411L21.9971 8.25234V4.75L21.9916 4.57583C21.9053 3.19357 20.7977 2.08813 19.4146 2.00502Z M6.202 11.764L6.21039 11.7435C6.21896 11.723 6.23351 11.6891 6.25449 11.644C6.2965 11.5535 6.36395 11.4182 6.46035 11.2529C6.65371 10.9214 6.95985 10.4758 7.40535 10.0303C8.28483 9.15085 9.7257 8.25 12 8.25C14.2743 8.25 15.7152 9.15085 16.5947 10.0303C17.0402 10.4758 17.3463 10.9214 17.5397 11.2529C17.6361 11.4182 1